\c 12
\s1 We napalimoya oijolo mololetokaka noiye.
\p 
\v 1 Omaimidanamu li elewole ikakamidana monawa li soto pebo wewena mukisiya li wego wego iki lilimi lagoli ikabo nenako, yamuya lowa-sawa niabo wewenasiya lolosa jikili sa-ikaka niabo nesamu ele-minoko eda lelokaka noibo nesaya ololoha oko le hulatune. Ito lahelamibo nesamidana nala likebo nesaki ololoha oko le hulatune. Sa-ominokote osele lelamideko anu lilipibotoya lolosa jeko wetune.
\v 2 Sa-ominoko ele elewole okakakumuya le omutokaka ito yamidana saina lalo le soto molokaka we Jisesiya makimidana oko lomudaloka nedeko, emotoka muda wehe lo-minoko lolosa jetune. Emokaho elowa jitibo nesamuya aha nesae loko elekadanaki, yoho yaha yalo nohelideko lahelamibo we ne litahe loko owana napa helibo nesa maya aha nesaya lolo okaiyoko miluma elidanaki heliye. Sa-okadanaki, Omaimidana onowelaki siyalo maya ade lamawaka yoweko ne.
\p 
\v 3 Lahelamibo nesahena ito hokoliyahena maya Jisesida lolo itabo maya ele hulikadanaki abuha molaiye. Sa-oneyo, edimosiya emokumu nieliki maya osele amilo. Sa-ikadeko dukatipoya wina okatiye.
\v 4 Ito edimosidaya lahelamibo nesalimo dilipe udakolo noiyoko, dabuha moliki lowa hi nibiki, dupalokaya itihina ayoko olada mako owaha amiye.
\v 5 Ito Omailimoya edimokumuya ipanele yuha minae loko lokadanaki, luhawatipo maya le ilitolibetaidanaki, ga mako lo libibo maya data molokaihe, olo. Sa-loko liye:
\q1 Emo ipanelika Omailimo ilime wehe lekolo oijolo moladekoma, yamuya ele hulamo.
\v 6 We napalimo ukala bekaka noibo wewenasida dilimeko dilipe wehe lokaka noiye. Ito mukilokaya oluhola lalo dilipe molaibosidaya oijo beko dilipe wehe lokaka noinako, lahelamibo nesamu auha emekadeko maya ukaka wina amideyo.
\m 
\v 7 We napalimoya oijolo mololibetokadekoma, osele iki dukadunuya eli aha nesa lolo amilo. Ito we makolimo oluholada kohako ilime wehe lametibo nehe, sako minamiye. Muki wewenasiya oluhonipolesidaya kohaidiki dilipi wehe likaka niabo nesama nenako, Omailimo mudaiboya emo oluhola lolo ikayoko, dilipe wehe lekoloya oijolo mololibetokaka noiye.
\v 8 Sakoya Omailimoya muki oluholalesidaya dilipe wehe lokaka noinako, edimosidaya sa-olibetamideko minataboya, oluhola lolo iki minamikilae. Ayauya lenenako anulo oluhone loko lekolaiye.
\v 9 Ito ga mako letuyo. Maya mikaukati ahotelesiya oijolo moli limikayoko maya, demega lamoko demesalo moludawo nesa maya ne. Sa-ominudawo nesa maya nenako, lukateya ahoteda lo meko minuniyoko wehe lokaiye. Sakokoteya mino lalotoka moloko minatune.
\v 10 Ahotelesiya edimonipo data elebotoya meleke amanamasi nowiyoko nowiyoko oijolo molilitikaka iki minikaka aboya, Omailimoya saina lalo limitiye loko ito eimola eto oko nebo ebatoka maya koliki minatae loko sa-oletakolaiye.
\v 11 Oijolo mololetoko lilime lalo okaka noibo nesaya soto pekaiyoko maya, ada eludawotoya lelamiyoko milumawaki nesa lolo okaka noiye. Ito alikaya mino wehe lokaka noudawolimoya saina laloya lemotoka hulukiya netibo ne.
\pi1 \bd 5-6\bd* Job 5:17; Plo 3:11-12
\s1 Omaimidana nasahilila maya mudai hulikatae loko data liye.
\p 
\v 12 Sa-onenako, edimoya duka opa ibo nesalimo di dadeu jekoko limiki udatabo nesa nolideko maya, osele amiki dabuha moliki elewole ilo.
\v 13 Monoka anugu wikili maya di lahelamibolimoya lina lahelamibo lolo oko suwokatiyo, monoka anuguya aku emesalo moliki niwideko wehe lokadekoma, Omaimidana anulaloya li wehe liki monilo.
\p 
\v 14 Edimoya muki wewenasitokaki hulu oko minatune liki ito duka laloki eto oko minatune likigo dabuha molalo. Ito duka huma jenebo wewenasiya miniki maya alika We napamidana mudamikilae.
\v 15 Edimokutiya we makomidanaya Omaimidana nasahililalimo asetokatiyo, ujapa iki minalo. Saniki apitipolokaya oloha lahelametibo makolimo isilika okaka noibomidana oko dukamidana ekesa nesalimo elewole okadeko, muki wewenasiya duka opa okatiyo, ujapa ibitiki minalo.
\v 16 Sa-nikiya edimotokatiya wewena mako ekahikaho Iso ibomidana okatiye. Pasidiyalo wewenasiya mini eto iki minamiki minikaka abomidana oko minokatiye. Isokahoya makoko nodenesamuye loko eimola makula ahulokati hulaiboma ne.
\v 17 Sa-onebo maya nenako, edimotipolita monawalamuya alo eli-minae. Emoya alikaya aholatokati maku lituwe loko lokaiyoko aholakaho o'e loko lo mekaiyoko, aya nesahena lolo-halo iboya nena nenako maya aya nesaya woko aha nesa lolo etiye loko elekadanaki, wije oko awisa loneboma ne.
\p 
\v 18 Edimoya Isilaelo wewena ileboya sa-ikiya Saenai bola li elikaka aweyaha amae. Ito Isilaelo wewenakidana iki jo ulumauya ma wiki hilamabo maya ne. Ito limu napa-napa viboku ito lubu jeneboku ito lasi ibokuya ma wamabo maya ne.
\v 19 Edimoya Saenai bolalokatiya pikuli napa jebo ito onowa napa liboya elamabo maya ne. Ito aya ga elebolawasiya ga makoki elametune likadanaki datauya oijo hiki letikiki minaboma ne.
\v 20 Ga sa-loko lo molaibo ga maya eleyoko eda delaiye: Wewena makoya aya bolalo monikadeko edimosiya ehadadunu kohaidi helitae. Ito jahenakiya asaikiya kohaidi helitae.
\v 21 Sakoya yatoka oliwaki nesaya soto piyoko, Mosesemamo mudakadanaki, yatoka nesamuya nemo oline nemekaiyoko luwo-luwo joe loko liye.
\p 
\v 22 Sa-oneboya, edimoya Jaiyoni bolalo nehekala, edimo Jaiyoni weuhauya Omaimidana numudala elewole oko minokakamidana ne eba Jelusalemukidana okulumau nebo ebatoya wiki hetikae. Sa-niadanaki, lepiki suwamitabo aweyaha iki okananipoki wewena minaboto,
\v 23 ito eimola oluhola lalo ulinipo okulumau luhuwa je molaiboki elowa jiki li nupa iki minabotoya wiki hetikae. Sa-nikiya muki wewena lihimatemu ona mololetatibo we Omai nebotoka wiki hetikae. Ito wehe liki minabo wewenasitoka wiki minikakaloka dilipe molaibo wewenasida weunipoloka koli mebo maya ne.
\v 24 Ito loko mutihibo ga ohatama maya le soto molokadanaki luwato nebo we Jisesitoka wiki hetikae. Ito Aeboloda koha helibo oladalalimoya yaloka paso loko liboto nehekala, Jisesikaho eimola oladala kisibolimoya leko yoweko saina lalomu lokaka noibo nesalo wiki hetikae.
\p 
\v 25 Eli-minahe. Ga lo libekaka noibo wemidanaya eli hulikatayo, ujapa iki minalo. Hapa yeikalaya Mosesekaho maya mikauka nedanaki ga mako lo bekaiyoko, eli aha nesa iki eli hulabo wewenasitokaya oliwaki nesaya dupalo soto pibo maya ne. Sa-okainako, olotiya okulumau nedanaki gala lo nolimibo wemidana lemesa mekudanaki gala ele hulatudawomuya bekimi oletamideko aha minatupe.
\v 26 Hapa ga noliyoko mima ibo ne. Sa-okaiyoko nenako, olotiya lomudaloya gala mako sa-loko lo molokaiye: Nemoya minoko aku maya mikayaki okulumakiya le momoga ekoloe, loko libo ne.
\v 27 Saina maina le soto molaibo maya le momoga okoko le tolowa etuwe loko elekadanaki liye. Sakoya le tolowa okadeko, elewole oko momoga amoko netibo nesahenaya soto pekoko elewole oko mino-loko woko minakolaiye.
\v 28 Lemoya ohola mako momoga ametibomidana mino-loko woko netibo nesaya le etoha ekolune. Aya nesamuya Omailoka epoka ludanaki oliwa mekaka oko Omailimo ele wati etibo nesa leko monokala loko minatune.
\v 29 Yaya nenahamuye, Omaiteya jo jeko ludokaka weya nenako, yamuyae.
\pi1 \bd 12\bd* Aes 35:3 \bd 13\bd* Plo 4:26 \bd 16\bd* Jen 25:29-34 \bd 17\bd* Jen 27:30-40
\pi1 \bd 18\bd* Eks 19:16-22; Eks 20:18-21; Dut 4:11-12; Dut 5:22-27
\pi1 \bd 20\bd* Eks 19:12-13 \bd 21\bd* Dut 9:19 \bd 24\bd* Jen 4:10 \bd 29\bd* Dut 4:24
\c 13
\s1 Oko moloko nouniyoko Omailimo ele wati etibo ga.
\p 
\v 1 Monokauya unala yala emo uka miyoko emo uka miyoko ikaka niabo nesaya li aha nesa lolo amilo.
\v 2 Wenoka wewenasida dilipi numudatipouka molatabo nesamuya osele delamideyo. Ito maloka wewenasiya wenoka wewena dilipe molupe likili okananipoki wewenasida maya dilipi moli-minaboma nenako loko noloe.
\v 3 Maloka wewenatipolesidaya monokamuye liki dilipi nala numuku molabosidamukiya elideko edimosidaki dilipi molabo elitiye. Saniki weunipoki miniki dilipi lahelibo lahelamibo ibitabo wewena mukiya eliki minalo.
\p 
\v 4 Anulo monikaka ito wesi mena ika iki olisa ikaka iki nimonebo wewenasidaya Omailimo lihima bitibo nenako, welo menalo minokaka nesatipoya wati nesa lolo noideko weki menaki koliki minatabo nesaya li opa amilo.
\v 5 We napalimoya nemo ma hulolibetamekoloe, ito hulo aito olibetamekoloe loko libo nenako, dukatipoya moni uvaminalo dabuha molamilo.
\v 6 Saina li-minabokumu lukaha amiki hulu ikigo li-minalo. Yamuya monoka bukuguya ga mako sa-liki luhuwa ji-minaboya ne:
\q1 We napaya nilime lalo okaka we maya nenako, nemoya yatoka matoka nesamuya oli nemamekolaiye. Wewenasiya nemodaya lahelametibo nesa nenahama lolo initadeko opa etuwe.
\m Lemoki aya luhuwa ji-minabo aya abuha-wowo le-minoko loko minatune.
\p 
\v 7 Ujapa wetipo Omaimidana ga wetome iki li bikaka abo wemu data kiki iki minatae. Sa-nikiya monoka anugu niwiki helebolawasida diyakau mudali hali niki edimotoka demesalo moliki eli elewole iki minatae.
\v 8 Jisesi Kalaestiya omutoko hapa yeikala nebo ito olotiya nebo, ito ayamidanago oko mino-loko woko minakolaiye.
\v 9 Sa-ekolaiyo, aya ga maya eli-miniki maya aito-aitomidana ohatama ga li nibideko maya elamilo. Omaimidana nasahililalimo luhawatipoya le ikitokadeko wati ekolaiye. Saina nokakamidana ito namo okakamidanamu ga li hukiminabolimoya lilime wati amekolaiye. Ya anulo wabo wewenasidaya yatoka nesalimoya ma dilimamibo ne.
\p 
\v 10 Lemodamuya Jisesima eimola upalaloti jokila he mekaka namabetautiya Juda wewenasi monokago li-minadanaki Omaimidana elekele itikaka niabo wewenasi natae loko ele bamiye.
\v 11 Yamuya edimo alo eli-minae. Omaitoka jokila he mekaka we napalimoya bulumaka ja ito meme ja kohaikadanaki, oladanipoloti lahelamibo lihimanipolo Omaitoka jokila hi mikaka monoka numuda napau leko yowekaiyoko, jawa maya ohuloka hetokaya liki limiki jo ji hulikaka niae.
\v 12 Ito Jisesiya asako eimola oladalalotiya wewena lukate le uluwitoletatuwe loko Jelusalemu numuda oho hetokaya kohaikayoko heliye.
\v 13 Yamuya lemo asako Juda wewenasi jokila hi mikaka abo nesa hulikiki lepa mutiwa letune loko Jisesitoka wetune. Ito sa-udawokidana lemo elowa jeko makomasi lemoto nisideko yamidana Jisesiya upalo elibomidana oko lupalo molikadeko aha eletune.
\v 14 Sa-loko noeleko sa-etune: Elewole eba mako lemotoka minamiye. Aha minoko soto pitibomuya ujapa okaka noune.
\v 15 Sa-onenako, Jisesida uliwa le sawa jekokoteya lepadunuya Omaimidana kolo meko epoka loko minatudawolimoya lemo Omaitoka jokila he mekaka nesate lolo okadeko, le Jisesida maya mekuniyoko le Omaimidana ilipitiye.
\v 16 Nasahiliki ito saina laloki moloko wewenasida betune liki data eli-minalo. Omailimoya yatoka nesamuya eliyoko emotoka jokila hi mebo nesa laloya lolo noiye.
\p 
\v 17 Duliki wetiposida ganipo maya elikiki emesalo moliki digukaya limiki minalo. Edimo weutipoloya li wehe liki ujapa iki minikaka niae. Aya yowanunipomidana monawaya alikaya li soto molakili yowanuya nile. Yamuya yowanunipoya duka lalototi litae liki sakiya elekele ibitalo. Miluma eliki sa-itaboya, dukatipouka wati etibo nesaya edimotoka soto pamekolaiye.
\p 
\v 18 Edimosiya lemodamuya Omailoka liki minalo. Lemoya eto okogo oko moloko etune loko labuha molokaka noune. Sakokoya lukauya lihima netibokumuya ohu jekaka noune.
\v 19 Omailoka likaka nesadunu nilimi wati ikadeko, We napalimo aku nilime wati okadeko, edimotoka enemane oko wetuwe loko noloe.
\pi1 \bd 2\bd* Jen 18:1-8; 19:1-3 \bd 5\bd* Dut 31:6,8; Jos 1:5 \bd 6\bd* Sam 118:6
\pi1 \bd 11\bd* Liv 16:27
\s1 Omaimidana epoka liye.
\p 
\v 20 Hulu ahola Omaiya We napate Jisesiya eimola oladaladunu elewole oko minokakamidana kolokaka ga le soto molaibomuye loko sipisipi jalo ujapa we napa lolo ibo we helibokuti aku ilime sinaibo weya ne.
\v 21 Emokahoya saina aito-aitomidana libeko dilipe lalo okadeko emokaho letibotoka molatibotoka iki eli litae loko noloe. Sa-nikiya emokaho ele wati etibo nesaya Jisesi Kalaestida abuha-wowolaloti le dukauya moladeyo. Emoya luhuwamidana aweyaha minadeko, epoka lowa lowa oko yowewa yowewa oko elewole oko netiye. Yotokoe.
\s1 Wewenasida dupamu elaiyoko lo biye.
\p 
\v 22 Wewenane yuhase, nemoya ga hana lo libamoe. Data leko luhawatipo le ikitetibo ga maya lo noliboyo, data ameme iki eli-minalo.
\v 23 Ito lo libekoloyo, eli-minalo. Wewenate Timotida maya nalauti alo olutimikae. Sa-ikanako, emoya enemane oko nisekadeko, ilime-loko woko mudaidasiye.
\v 24 Ujapa wetipo ito muki Jisesida wewenalasida dupamu nelokaiyoko noloyo, li bilo. Italiya mikaukati wewenatipolesiya dupamu delokaiyoko lo noliboe.
\v 25 Omaimidana nasahilila edimotoka mino-loko woko minadeyo. 
